 Output demo.gif
  Set Width 1200
  Set Height 800

  Type "clover add ~/code/clover"
  Enter
  Sleep 1s

  Type "clover add ~/code/my-app --name frontend"
  Enter
  Sleep 1s

  Type "clover focus clover"
  Enter
  Sleep 500ms

  Type "clover list"
  Enter
  Sleep 2s

  Type "clover session --focus --dry-run"
  Enter
  Sleep 7s